---

## Overview

The HR/Recruitment team needs a centralized Salesforce system to manage the end-to-end recruitment lifecycle, powered by AI for intelligent candidate matching.

---

## Core Business Needs

1. **Job Management** — Post and manage job openings with full lifecycle (Draft → Open → Closed).
2. **Candidate Database** — Maintain a searchable candidate database with resumes, skills, and experience.
3. **Application Tracking (ATS)** — Track every application from submission to hiring decision.
4. **Interview Coordination** — Schedule, conduct, and record interview feedback across multiple rounds.
5. **AI-Powered Screening** — Use Agentforce to auto-score candidates against job requirements.
6. **Offer Management** — Automated approval workflows for offer letters above defined thresholds.
7. **Email Automation** — Auto-send updates to candidates, recruiters, and managers.
8. **Reporting & Analytics** — Dashboards for time-to-hire, conversion rate, source effectiveness.

---

## Stakeholders

| Role | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| HR Manager | Approves job postings & offers |
| Recruiter | Manages candidates & interviews |
| Interviewer | Submits interview feedback |
| Candidate (external) | Applies to jobs |

---

## Success Metrics

- 50% reduction in time-to-hire
- 80% accuracy in AI candidate matching
- 100% offer approval traceability
- 30% improvement in recruiter productivity




Action: file_editor create /app/AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment-Salesforce/01-Requirements/Project-Scope.md --file-text "# Project Scope

GitHub Link: `https://github.com/<your-username>/AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment-Salesforce/blob/main/01-Requirements/Project-Scope.md`

---

## In Scope

### Custom Objects
- `Job__c` — Job postings
- `Candidate__c` — Candidate database
- `Application__c` — Junction object for applications
- `Interview__c` — Interview records
- `Offer__c` — Offer letters

### Salesforce Configuration
- Validation rules for data integrity
- Approval process for offer letters
- Record-triggered flows for automation
- Email templates & alerts
- Custom page layouts & dynamic forms
- Lightning App (\"Recruitment Hub\")

### AI / Custom Code
- Agentforce AI agent for candidate scoring
- Apex classes for AI integration
- Custom LWC for AI match visualization

### Security
- 3 Profiles (Recruiter, HR Manager, Interviewer)
- Role hierarchy
- Duplicate & matching rules
- Permission sets

### Deployment
- SFDX project setup
- GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline
- UAT test cases

---

## Out of Scope

- External job board integration (LinkedIn, Indeed, Naukri)
- Payroll module
- Native mobile app (Phase 2)
- Background verification integration
- E-signature for offer letters
- Multi-language support
- Video interview platform integration

---

## Assumptions

- Salesforce Enterprise/Unlimited Edition with Einstein/Agentforce licenses
- Internet access for AI callouts
- Email deliverability is configured at org level
- All users have valid Salesforce licenses

---

## Constraints

- Apex governor limits (CPU time, callouts)
- Agentforce API rate limits
- Daily email send limit (5,000 per org for Standard)

---

## Deliverables

| # | Deliverable |
|---|-------------|
| 1 | Configured Salesforce org with all custom objects |
| 2 | Working Agentforce AI agent |
| 3 | Lightning App with full UI |
| 4 | User documentation |
| 5 | Deployment scripts & CI/CD pipeline |
| 6 | UAT sign-off |

---

## Timeline (Indicative)

| Phase | Duration |
|-------|----------|
| Planning | 1 week |
| Backend Build | 3 weeks |
| AI Integration | 2 weeks |
| UI/UX | 2 weeks |
| Security & Testing | 1 week |
| Deployment & UAT | 1 week |
| **Total** | **10 weeks** |
